GameBoard - Class in cpsc2150.extendedConnectX.models
This class determines what characters are at certain positions and places tokens into the board.
GameBoard(int, int, int) - Constructor for class cpsc2150.extendedConnectX.models.GameBoard
Creates a 2-dimensional array of characters where position [0][0] would be the bottom left of the board and [ROW - 1][COLUMN - 1] would be the top right of the board; all with blank characters.
